---
import ContentPage from '../layouts/ContentPage.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: `${SITE.url}/` },
  { name: 'Contact', url: `${SITE.url}/contact/` },
];
---
<ContentPage
  title="Contact"
  description="Get in touch with the Pool Shock Calculator team — corrections, product strengths to add, and general questions."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <p>
    We read everything and especially want to hear about anything that looks
    inaccurate. Reader corrections help keep the dosing math honest.
  </p>

  <h2>Email us</h2>
  <p>
    The fastest way to reach us is by email at
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>. To help us respond well,
    please include:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The page you were using (for example, the green pool or liquid chlorine calculator).</li>
    <li>Your pool volume, the product and strength you selected, and the result you got.</li>
    <li>What you expected instead, and any source you’re comparing against.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Suggest a product or feature</h2>
  <p>
    Using a shock product whose strength isn’t in our list? Send the product name and
    its available-chlorine percentage from the label and we’ll look at adding it. We
    also welcome suggestions for new situations or calculators.
  </p>

  <h2>A note on advice</h2>
  <p>
    We’re glad to help you understand how the calculator works, but we can’t
    diagnose a specific pool remotely or provide professional or medical advice. For
    stubborn water problems, a local pool professional who can test your water in
    person is your best bet.
  </p>
</ContentPage>
